"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?14/8/14472/contributors\">",
"     Hannah Lee, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?14/8/14472/contributors\">",
"     Kris V Kowdley, MD, FACP, FACG, FASGE, AGAF",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
"   <div>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials contributorType\" href=\"UTD.htm?14/8/14472/contributors\">",
"     Section Editor",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?14/8/14472/contributors\">",
"     Sanjiv Chopra, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
"   <div>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials contributorType\" href=\"UTD.htm?14/8/14472/contributors\">",
